I expect none of us like all the recent attacks, insults, accusations, threats, hurting of feelings, and attempts to piss people off.   

Can I suggest we stick to the purpose of the group: &quot;the discussion, promotion, and developemnt of Electronic Voice Phenomenon, and Instrumental Transcommunication methods and technologies as used in the communication with spirit, and other entities.&quot;

And that we go with Frank&#39;s philosophy &quot;just take the approach, try different methods, see what works.&quot;

No more threats.  No name calling, insults, or accusations.  Just try to keep a positive group attitude, be open that not everyone believes what everyone else does, and that&#39;s ok?
